#Sample Feature Definition Template
@tag
Feature:Your Payments
  @tag1
  Scenario: Checking for the functionality of Your Payments
    Given User must be on his /her account page
    And Click on Login Message
    When On Clicking on Your payments option must navigate to Add Payment method
    
    Then User must be able to click on Add a Credit or Debit card

  